Title: Jewerly for grandma
Description: Dear grandma, I know you are angry at me because I did not go to your birthday anniversary party and won't cook me cepelinai for that, but look: got you your favourite jewerly, we can now reconcile :).

Title: Keys of the car
Description: Hey dude, thanks for letting me use your car. Sorry I have accidently forgot to give back you your keys. I know you live in your car and past few days should have been rough for you, but hey, I am bringing your keys back. Don't catch a cold.

Title: Face masks
Description: Hey friend, you are as lazy as always. Afraid to catch Covid yet too lazy to go get you some mask. So here, I am gifting a ton of them to you. Stay safe and healthy.

Title: Fart of the celebrity in the jar
Description: Dude, I don't know why you need this useless thing, but you have requested it so I am obliged to give it to you. Here, get it, QUICKLY!

Title: Bicycle computer "Sigma"
Description: Thank you for your purchase. You are contributing to the healthier tomorrow by not polluting the environment!

Title: Lego police station
Description: Thanks for the purchase. Here is your police Lego station oh great lawful constructor!

Title: PocketBook reader
Description: Here friend, I know you are very mean and like to pirate stuff, so I am bringing you (actually not I, but the effort is the same) a pocket book reader. However, take my advice, I is always better to read books the classic way. Don't care for the trees, care for the nostalgia as I do!

Title: "Ace combat 7" game disc
Description: The legendary flying game is coming to you! It should arrive shorty! Remember to buy a good joystick for that. You can do this in your shop :).

Title: Driving license
Description: Greetings. Congrats for passing the exam. The driving license if coming to you. Drive safely.
